<subSubSection id="C6C57ACAFFDCFFE8FF28FD6A436D1AD2" pageId="2" pageNumber="487" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="8E602941FFDCFFE8FF28FD6A436D1AD2" blockId="2.[159,781,662,1163]" pageId="2" pageNumber="487">
<emphasis id="BCABF553FFDCFFE8FF28FD6A40421A73" bold="true" box="[159,275,758,781]" pageId="2" pageNumber="487">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
The species may be differentiated from other members of the 
<taxonomicName id="49DF52C2FFDCFFE8FEE4FC8A437B1A53" baseAuthorityName="Walch" baseAuthorityYear="1775" box="[339,554,790,813]" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Astraptes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="487" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fulgerator">
<emphasis id="BCABF553FFDCFFE8FEE4FC8A437B1A53" box="[339,554,790,813]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="487">Astraptes fulgerator</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
complex by the following combination of character states of the DNA barcode: 38 
<collectionCode id="E8CEB184FFDCFFE8FF4DFCCA405D1A13" box="[250,268,854,877]" name="Tavera, Department of Geology and Geophysics" pageId="2" pageNumber="487">T</collectionCode>
; 52 
<collectionCode id="E8CEB184FFDCFFE8FE85FCCA40121A13" box="[306,323,854,877]" name="Tavera, Department of Geology and Geophysics" pageId="2" pageNumber="487">T</collectionCode>
; 202 
<collectionCode id="E8CEB184FFDCFFE8FECFFCCA40D81A13" box="[376,393,854,877]" name="Tavera, Department of Geology and Geophysics" pageId="2" pageNumber="487">T</collectionCode>
; 205C; 274 
<collectionCode id="E8CEB184FFDCFFE8FDB3FCCA43441A13" box="[516,533,854,877]" name="Tavera, Department of Geology and Geophysics" pageId="2" pageNumber="487">T</collectionCode>
; 568A. 202 
<collectionCode id="E8CEB184FFDCFFE8FD38FCCA43CE1A13" box="[655,671,854,877]" name="Tavera, Department of Geology and Geophysics" pageId="2" pageNumber="487">T</collectionCode>
